                    "text": "**Running SQL query for average price**\n\nI need to run a query to find the average extended price, grouped by nation. To do this, I\u2019ll join the lineitem table to orders using the order key, then connect orders to customers with the customer key, and finally link customers to nations through the nation key. The goal is to compute the average price using SQL effectively. Let\u2019s get started!"
